 The plane, <ORGANIZATION> USAir </ORGANIZATION> Flight 5050, a <ORGANIZATION> Boeing </ORGANIZATION> 737-400, went down on takeoff from <LOCATION> LaGuardia </LOCATION>, bound for <LOCATION> Charlotte </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> N.C. </LOCATION>, said <PERSON> Susan </PERSON> <PERSON> Young </PERSON>, a <ORGANIZATION> USAir </ORGANIZATION> spokewoman in <LOCATION> Pittsburgh </LOCATION>. `` On takeoff it went off the end of the runway and it is now partially submerged in the water,'' she said. Young had no information about the number of people aboard or possible injuries.
