<HEAD>EDs: Stands for AM-Bush-Carter listed on the AM News Digest</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JIM DRINKARD</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Asspcoated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
