 to encourage him in his observer effort, ask that he try to get the <ORGANIZATION> Sandinistas </ORGANIZATION> to allow other observers down there as well,'' said White House Press Secretary <PERSON> Marlin </PERSON> <PERSON> Fitzwater </PERSON>. The leftist government has blocked some other international observers.
